{"tid":1782122,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"坐飛機耳仔痛到爆炸","createTime":"2019-12-13T16:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T12:34:41.000Z","uid":312419,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"3fab929c367bd24f4f2fb7fb5fc4c190c11c742f","tid":1782122,"uid":312419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:38:22.000Z","msg":"好想知有冇人都係咁<br />\n次次坐飛機耳仔都痛到爆炸<br />\n唔係起飛同降落嗰隻痛<br />\n係差唔多落機前30-45分鐘就開始痛<br />\n大概開始由最高點慢慢降落（？）<br />\n有次痛到喊出嚟<br />\n真係好困擾 <br />\n睇醫生話係鼻敏感導致<br />\n但我已經坐飛機前2星期食鼻敏感藥<br />\n有冇人有相同情況 但有解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ee66df8799fa17430074909d2219849e5cd348","tid":1782122,"uid":201414,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"通空姐講 跟住佢會帶你入廁所 之後會輕鬆曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d1fb69db6312a5be0e4de72e32fdda2f5c5aab","tid":1782122,"uid":51057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:41:20.000Z","msg":"用手摙實個鼻再噴氣"},{"pid":"630f235c27d31de1d7485688574b5110a23eba1e","tid":1782122,"uid":25557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:42:18.000Z","msg":"合埋個口鍊住個鼻再呼氣，平衡返個氣壓"},{"pid":"ddc7401ad4169ce50ef9059221e86976870196cf","tid":1782122,"uid":312419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"09d1fb69db6312a5be0e4de72e32fdda2f5c5aab","tid":1782122,"uid":51057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:41:20.000Z","msg":"用手摙實個鼻再噴氣"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:43:27.000Z","msg":"冇用<br />\n呑口水同食糖都冇用<br />\n嗰隻痛好似入面血管充晒血<br />\n真係覺得耳仔要爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca6004751510f8fcc62f1c87e17bcbc9229ceaf","tid":1782122,"uid":335391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ddc7401ad4169ce50ef9059221e86976870196cf","tid":1782122,"uid":312419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"09d1fb69db6312a5be0e4de72e32fdda2f5c5aab","tid":1782